"{\"uid\": \"deccanchronicle.com-world-olympics-opening-ceremony-a-disgrace-donald-trump-1813228\", \"text\": \"Washington:Former US president Donald Trump has criticised the opening ceremony of the Summer Olympics in Paris, calling it a \\\"disgrace\\\", amidst outrage over a scene which critics say parodied Leonardo da Vinci's acclaimed painting \\\"The Last Supper.\\\"\"}"